765
00:48:19,360 --> 00:48:20,760
Mr. Friedman.

766
00:48:22,000 --> 00:48:24,100
Well done.

767
00:48:25,000 --> 00:48:27,300
Well done.
Let's go.

768
00:48:29,010 --> 00:48:31,140
Why are you smiling?

769
00:48:31,140 --> 00:48:33,980
