772
00:48:38,750 --> 00:48:40,520
A word with you, Friedman.

773
00:48:40,520 --> 00:48:42,480
Yes, of course.

774
00:48:42,490 --> 00:48:43,890
Alone.

775
00:48:45,150 --> 00:48:47,360
Or to you both.

776
00:48:47,360 --> 00:48:50,760
The doctor who examined Ellie
is testifying tomorrow.

777
00:48:50,760 --> 00:48:53,600
It's rather personal, of course.

778
00:48:53,600 --> 00:48:54,900
These are private people...

779
00:48:54,900 --> 00:48:57,000
Please get to the point.

780
00:48:57,000 --> 00:48:58,330
Excuse me?

781
00:49:00,240 --> 00:49:03,240
I've spoken with John Strubing,
and he's willing to consider a plea.

782
00:49:03,240 --> 00:49:04,910
It's my decision, of course,

783
00:49:04,910 --> 00:49:07,580
but plead your boy and I'll recommend
a sentence of 20 years.

784
00:49:07,580 --> 00:49:09,480
- Otherwise, he gets life.
- No.

785
00:49:10,610 --> 00:49:12,510
No deals.

786
00:49:14,220 --> 00:49:16,150
Mr. Friedman?

787
00:49:17,420 --> 00:49:19,390
Not my call.

788
00:49:19,390 --> 00:49:21,860
Of course. You have to
speak to your client.

789
00:49:21,860 --> 00:49:24,330
I'll expect a different answer
in the morning.

790
00:49:28,800 --> 00:49:30,530
Even with good behavior,

791
00:49:30,530 --> 00:49:32,940
you'd be locked up
at least 14 years.

792
00:49:34,740 --> 00:49:36,670
I could maybe do that.

793
00:49:40,210 --> 00:49:42,380
They don't know we found the cop,
Joseph.

794
00:49:43,710 --> 00:49:45,780
We don't even know
if Strubing will show up.

795
00:49:45,780 --> 00:49:48,880
- You could walk out of here a free man.
- But if she does...

796
00:49:48,890 --> 00:49:50,390
- If you wrong...
- Listen.

797
00:49:50,390 --> 00:49:52,690
The decision is yours.
Sam.

798
00:49:54,160 --> 00:49:56,590
I need to talk to Joseph.

799
00:49:56,590 --> 00:49:59,800
- Are you asking me to leave?
- Of course not.

800
00:49:59,800 --> 00:50:01,960
He's your client.

801
00:50:01,970 --> 00:50:03,870
I'm asking you to listen.

802
00:50:08,810 --> 00:50:11,170
When we first met,

803
00:50:11,180 --> 00:50:13,200
I told you I'd only
defend you if you were

804
00:50:13,210 --> 00:50:15,340
