me you were innocent.

805
00:50:15,350 --> 00:50:18,450
You remember?
I remember.

806
00:50:18,450 --> 00:50:21,420
Did you lie to me?
No, I didn't lie.

807
00:50:21,420 --> 00:50:25,220
So I'm gonna ask you again.
Did you commit this crime?

808
00:50:26,490 --> 00:50:29,660
No.
But you're willing to say you did.

809
00:50:29,660 --> 00:50:31,990
If I got to.
For the deal.

810
00:50:32,000 --> 00:50:33,860
If you "got to"?

811
00:50:39,270 --> 00:50:41,940
My great-granddaddy
was a slave.

812
00:50:44,210 --> 00:50:46,240
Were your people slaves, Joseph?

813
00:50:47,810 --> 00:50:50,880
When we were slaves we had to do
what the master said.

814
00:50:50,880 --> 00:50:53,850
But... we're not slaves now,
are we?

815
00:50:53,850 --> 00:50:56,180
No, we ain't slaves.

816
00:50:56,190 --> 00:50:58,320
You say that like it's nothin'.

817
00:50:58,320 --> 00:51:02,620
We ain't slaves because we rose up and
we fought and we fought and we fought

818
00:51:02,630 --> 00:51:04,260
till we got our freedom.

819
00:51:05,330 --> 00:51:07,230
Isn't that right?

820
00:51:09,130 --> 00:51:11,700
My granddaddy escaped
when he was 15.

821
00:51:13,200 --> 00:51:16,200
Fought off four men and an attack dog,
my mama said.

822
00:51:16,210 --> 00:51:19,670
Okay, then you tell me this.

823
00:51:19,680 --> 00:51:22,380
After what your granddaddy did
to get his freedom,

824
00:51:22,380 --> 00:51:25,910
you're just gonna give it right back
for nothing,

825
00:51:25,920 --> 00:51:27,780
for something
you didn't even do?

826
00:51:29,350 --> 00:51:31,220
Understand this.

827
00:51:31,220 --> 00:51:34,890
If you want your freedom,
you're gonna have to fight for it.

828
00:51:34,890 --> 00:51:37,660
But you don't have to fight alone.
That's why I'm here.

829
00:51:38,900 --> 00:51:41,160
We've got weapons now, Joseph.

830
00:51:41,170 --> 00:51:43,700
Our people do.

831
00:51:43,700 --> 00:51:45,600
Weapons we didn't have before.

832
00:51:48,570 --> 00:51:50,510
We've got the law.

833
00:51:51,670 --> 00:51:54,780
And you've got Sam,

834
00:51:54,780 --> 00:51:59,950
one of the finest young trial lawyers
in this country, on your side.

835
00:52:03,350 --> 00:52:05,190
You really think we can win?

836
00:52:07,390 --> 00:52:10,160
I wouldn't be here if I didn't think
we could win.

837
00:52:14,230 --> 00:52:17,000
Dr. Sayer, please tell the jury
your field of specialty.

838
00:52:18,230 --> 00:52:20,900
I specialize
in the field of gynecology,

839
00:52:20,900 --> 00:52:24,270
and I deliver babies.

840
00:52:24,270 --> 00:52:24,940
Aww!

841
00:52:24,950 --> 00:52:26,980
On the morning she was
discovered in the reservoir,

842
00:52:26,980 --> 00:52:30,910
did you have occasion to examine
Mrs. Eleanor Strubing?

843
00:52:30,910 --> 00:52:32,610
Yes.

844
00:52:32,620 --> 00:52:35,550
She was brought to my home
by the police at, uh...

845
00:52:36,720 --> 00:52:39,860
Let's see.
6:30 in the morning.

846
00:52:40,920 --> 00:52:42,690
Did she tell you
what had happened?

847
00:52:44,260 --> 00:52:45,990
Objection. Hearsay.

848
00:52:46,000 --> 00:52:47,960
Overruled.

849
00:52:47,970 --> 00:52:49,400
Doctor?

850
00:52:50,400 --> 00:52:52,670
I've forgotten the question.

851
00:52:52,670 --> 00:52:54,470
What did Mrs. Strubing
tell you?

852
00:52:55,740 --> 00:52:58,170
She told me
that she had been raped

853
00:52:58,180 --> 00:53:00,210
by a colored man
who worked for her.

854
00:53:02,180 --> 00:53:05,980
What was her mental state
during all of this?

855
00:53:05,980 --> 00:53:09,920
She was severely distraught,
weeping.

856
00:53:09,920 --> 00:53:13,490
She kept repeating, "Am I pregnant?
Am I pregnant?"

857
00:53:14,690 --> 00:53:17,860
- Did you then examine her?
- Yes.

858
00:53:17,860 --> 00:53:20,860
My wife assisted
by removing her clothing.

859
00:53:20,860 --> 00:53:23,700
It was torn, wet, and muddy.

860
00:53:24,930 --> 00:53:28,500
I noted bruises
on her arms and legs

861
00:53:28,510 --> 00:53:31,410
and numerous abrasions and contusions
on both extremities.

862
00:53:32,540 --> 00:53:34,880
I then performed
an internal exam.

863
00:53:34,880 --> 00:53:38,110
Do you have an opinion,
based upon reasonable medical certainty,

864
00:53:38,120 --> 00:53:40,280
as to whether or not
she had been raped?

865
00:53:41,780 --> 00:53:43,350
Beyond question,
Mr. Willis.

866
00:53:43,350 --> 00:53:46,760
It was all consistent with rape.

867
00:53:48,490 --> 00:53:49,930
Thank you.

868
00:53:51,030 --> 00:53:52,690
Your witness.

869
00:53:52,700 --> 00:53:54,630
Get the records.

870
00:53:56,230 --> 00:53:58,030
Medical records.
Get them.

871
00:53:58,040 --> 00:54:00,240
