These are personal.

873
00:54:04,140 --> 00:54:05,840
Overruled.

874
00:54:05,840 --> 00:54:08,910
I'm sorry, Mr. Willis,
but the witness referred to them.

875
00:54:08,910 --> 00:54:11,280
- They must be turned over.
- Thank you, Your Honor.

876
00:54:12,520 --> 00:54:14,450
