could it not?

882
00:54:49,020 --> 00:54:50,250
It's possible.

883
00:55:01,100 --> 00:55:04,000
You did an internal exam
and you found...

884
00:55:05,370 --> 00:55:08,770
"edema, swelling,
traces of blood."

885
00:55:08,770 --> 00:55:11,270
- Yes.
- Mm-hmm.

886
00:55:11,280 --> 00:55:14,810
And it was based on this that you
determined that she was raped?

887
00:55:14,810 --> 00:55:16,810
Indeed.

888
00:55:16,810 --> 00:55:18,350
But those same findings...

889
00:55:19,780 --> 00:55:22,380
are equally consistent
with a woman who took a lover

890
00:55:22,390 --> 00:55:25,550
and engaged in vigorous sexual intercourse
over the course of an evening.

891
00:55:25,560 --> 00:55:28,820
Objection. How dare you.
There is no evidence of any lover.

892
00:55:28,830 --> 00:55:30,430
Sustained.

893
00:55:30,430 --> 00:55:33,400
There's no place for that in my courtroom,
Mr. Friedman.

894
00:55:34,730 --> 00:55:37,270
Um, of course, Your Honor.

895
00:55:37,270 --> 00:55:39,870
I-I'm sorry.

896
00:55:49,180 --> 00:55:51,750
- Hello?
- Hey, baby.

897
00:55:53,080 --> 00:55:55,350
No, they just pulled me
out of proceedings.

898
00:55:55,350 --> 00:55:56,890
The baby...

899
00:55:58,620 --> 00:56:00,220
didn't make it.

900
00:56:02,990 --> 00:56:06,560
And it was just so much worse this time.
The bleeding was just...

901
00:56:07,530 --> 00:56:08,960
It wouldn't stop.

902
00:56:08,970 --> 00:56:10,270
I'm so sorry.

903
00:56:12,840 --> 00:56:14,870
I should be there.

904
00:56:20,280 --> 00:56:21,610
Buster?

905
00:56:23,810 --> 00:56:25,280
Buster, are you there?

906
00:56:26,350 --> 00:56:27,750
Yeah, I'm...

907
00:56:29,320 --> 00:56:30,690
I'm here.

908
00:56:32,520 --> 00:56:33,920
Where are you?

909
00:56:37,830 --> 00:56:40,130
Do you have any further questions,
Mr. Friedman?

910
00:56:58,680 --> 00:57:01,480
Mrs. Strubing told you
that she resisted her assailant?

911
00:57:01,490 --> 00:57:03,390
Yes, she did.
Mm-hmm.

912
00:57:03,390 --> 00:57:05,850
And you looked under her fingernails
too, didn't you,

913
00:57:05,860 --> 00:57:07,920
to see if you could find
any traces of skin?

914
00:57:07,920 --> 00:57:09,420
I did.

915
00:57:09,430 --> 00:57:12,230
What did you find?

916
00:57:12,230 --> 00:57:14,400
Splinters, dirt in some...

917
00:57:14,400 --> 00:57:16,530
- Any skin, Doctor?
- No, Sam.

918
00:57:16,530 --> 00:57:19,370
Yes. I was just
about to get to that.

919
00:57:19,370 --> 00:57:21,340
Excuse me?

920
00:57:21,340 --> 00:57:22,800
There was skin.

921
00:57:26,240 --> 00:57:28,710
Wh-Where...

922
00:57:28,710 --> 00:57:32,780
Where in these records does it say anything
about finding traces of skin?

923
00:57:32,780 --> 00:57:35,920
It's not in the records.

924
00:57:35,920 --> 00:57:40,020
My wife took the notes. She did not
write down that bit of information.

925
00:57:42,120 --> 00:57:44,860
Why not, Doctor?
Why would she not record that?

926
00:57:46,460 --> 00:57:50,370
Out of respect for the patient's privacy,
Mr. Friedman.

927
00:57:51,870 --> 00:57:53,970
It was the skin
of a colored man.

928
00:57:59,440 --> 00:58:01,640
No further questions.

929
00:58:01,650 --> 00:58:05,110
It wasn't in the records.
They got a doctor to lie under oath.

930
00:58:05,120 --> 00:58:06,680
How do we fight against that?

931
00:58:07,780 --> 00:58:09,820
You asked the exact question

932
00:58:09,820 --> 00:58:11,750
Willis wanted you to ask.

933
00:58:11,760 --> 00:58:14,660
- What were you thinking?
- Where the hell were you? Hmm?

934
00:58:14,660 --> 00:58:16,560
Getting instructions
from Walter White?

935
00:58:16,560 --> 00:58:19,930
See what happens when I don't hold
your hand? You panic like an amateur.

936
00:58:19,930 --> 00:58:22,230
You should have let him
take the deal.

937
00:58:22,230 --> 00:58:26,070
Goddamn it, would you shut up about
the deal? We have an alibi witness.

938
00:58:26,070 --> 00:58:27,640
What don't you get?

939
00:58:27,640 --> 00:58:31,510
They will have McCoy change his testimony.
Just watch.

940
00:58:31,510 --> 00:58:35,110
Let them. We'll take his sworn statement
and shove it up his ass.

941
00:58:35,110 --> 00:58:39,080
No, tomorrow morning I'm asking Willis
if the offer is still on the table.

942
00:58:39,080 --> 00:58:42,250
The NAACP
isn't taking any deals.

943
00:58:42,250 --> 00:58:45,000
The NAACP isn't the one with
its life on the line here.

944
00:58:45,020 --> 00:58:46,250
Yes, it is, goddamn it.

945
00:58:50,160 --> 00:58:52,830
You're using him.

946
00:58:52,830 --> 00:58:54,760
That's all this is.

947
00:58:54,760 --> 00:58:56,870
Just like you said
the Communists would.

948
00:58:56,870 --> 00:59:00,700
We're giving him the best possible defense
under the circumstances.

949
00:59:00,700 --> 00:59:02,800
Mmm. Yeah.

950
00:59:02,810 --> 00:59:06,770
I'm sure he'll feel really lucky as
he sits in prison for the rest of his life.

951
00:59:06,780 --> 00:59:09,940
Let's not act like it's Joseph Spell you're
concerned for all of a sudden.

952
00:59:09,950 --> 00:59:12,450
