953
00:59:12,450 --> 00:59:15,780
From the moment you got involved in this,
you've been looking for a way out.

954
00:59:15,790 --> 00:59:18,650
Play nice with the DA,
earn yourself a favor,

955
00:59:18,660 --> 00:59:21,520
maybe they'll let you in their neighborhood
or their club one day.

956
00:59:21,530 --> 00:59:23,730
Well, get this
through your head.

957
00:59:23,730 --> 00:59:26,730
The only way to get through a bigot's door
is to break it down.

958
00:59:29,200 --> 00:59:32,330
Must be easy
for you to say, huh?

959
00:59:32,340 --> 00:59:35,140
See, it's my life
that is on the line here.

960
00:59:35,140 --> 00:59:38,040
My family, my practice,
my future.

961
00:59:38,040 --> 00:59:42,910
What do you have?
You have nothing to lose.

962
00:59:42,910 --> 00:59:47,550
No, you just sweep through town,
stirring up all kinds of ugliness,

963
00:59:47,550 --> 00:59:49,480
then move right on.

964
00:59:51,050 --> 00:59:54,960
No one will ever
even remember you were here.

965
00:59:57,060 --> 00:59:59,630
Oh, fuck you, Sam.

966
01:00:01,530 --> 01:00:03,460
Fuck you.

967
01:00:22,850 --> 01:00:25,590
Hey.
You two okay?

968
01:00:39,030 --> 01:00:41,470
Please take the stand,
Mrs. Strubing.

969
01:00:52,920 --> 01:00:54,880
Mrs. Strubing,
you reside in Greenwich?

970
01:00:56,790 --> 01:01:02,560
Yes. My husband John and I moved
from Philadelphia about a year ago.

971
01:01:02,560 --> 01:01:05,560
Is your husband here
in the courtroom today?

972
01:01:05,560 --> 01:01:07,160
Of course.

973
01:01:07,160 --> 01:01:09,060
Sitting in the front.

974
01:01:11,230 --> 01:01:16,670
Mrs. Strubing, do you remember the night
you were attacked?

975
01:01:16,670 --> 01:01:19,240
Mr. Willis, I assure you,
I will never forget it.

976
01:01:21,010 --> 01:01:22,710
Please tell the jury
what happened.

977
01:01:25,810 --> 01:01:29,620
My husband was away on business,

978
01:01:29,620 --> 01:01:33,190
as he is often, I'm afraid.

979
01:01:33,190 --> 01:01:36,420
I had dinner with friends...
the Moores.

980
01:01:36,430 --> 01:01:40,830
And I arrived home
around ten o'clock

981
01:01:40,830 --> 01:01:44,500
and then I decided
to shower before bed.

982
01:01:44,500 --> 01:01:48,000
And I was fixing my hair.

983
01:01:49,670 --> 01:01:52,670
And he came in the room.

984
01:01:52,680 --> 01:01:55,340
He came after me
and started chasing me.

985
01:01:59,720 --> 01:02:01,450
He had a knife.

986
01:02:01,450 --> 01:02:03,620
The knife was pointed
at my throat,

987
01:02:03,620 --> 01:02:06,020
and I...

988
01:02:06,020 --> 01:02:07,960
I thought of screaming, but...

989
01:02:09,220 --> 01:02:10,960
I couldn't.

990
01:02:10,960 --> 01:02:13,230
He... He penetrated me.

991
01:02:14,160 --> 01:02:15,800
I couldn't make him stop.

992
01:02:17,000 --> 01:02:19,230
His body was crushing me.

993
01:02:20,570 --> 01:02:22,470
What happened next,
Mrs. Strubing?

994
01:02:25,810 --> 01:02:28,180
He said he wasn't finished
with me.

995
01:02:30,810 --> 01:02:32,380
And then he did it again.

996
01:02:32,380 --> 01:02:34,720
Did what?

997
01:02:37,320 --> 01:02:38,820
Raped me, Mr. Willis.

998
01:02:40,220 --> 01:02:42,420
And then what happened?

999
01:02:42,430 --> 01:02:47,330
When it was over, he said,
"We're going for a ride, Mrs. Strubing."

1000
01:02:47,330 --> 01:02:49,600
After all that,

1001
01:02:49,600 --> 01:02:52,070
he still called me
"Mrs. Strubing."

1002
01:02:53,770 --> 01:02:55,970
Then he tore my dress
